pfring kernel module configuration

node.cfg generator for number of nics and cpus
broctl generator, prompt for MailTo etc.



from septun:

for each interface:
ethtool -L $IF combined 1
ethtool -G $IF rx 512
ethtool -C $IF adaptive-rx on rx-usecs 100



set to UTC and setup NTP.


interfacesetup.enabled = 1
pfringclusterid=11 in broctl.cfg
